    StorageElement

    public class LfuStorageElement
extends AccessHistoryStorageElement
    A StorageElement where the file to delete is chosen using a Least Frequently Used (LFU) algorithm.

      • filesToDelete

        public java.util.List filesToDelete(DataFile newFile)
        Returns the DataFiles which have been accessed least frequently in recent access history. If there is a file on the SE which is not in the access history this is used first since it has been accessed the least number of times (ie zero).
        Specified by:
